            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Neither works without the other. On-page SEO makes your content crawlable and relevant. Off-page SEO gives it the authority to rank. For competitive keywords, strong off-page signals are often the differentiator — the #1 result has 3.8x more backlinks than positions 2-10 (Backlinko).</p></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
