              <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Purchasing low-quality backlinks from link farms, private blog networks, or link-exchange schemes. Google's Penguin and manual action systems are specifically designed to detect and penalise artificial link patterns. One manual penalty can remove a site from search results for months.</p></div></div>
